OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FShetland will be cloudy with
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain, more persistent in
OL,7,Fthe morning. Orkney rather cloudy with
OL,8,Fsome brighter spells, but also a few
OL,9,Fshowers. Fresh to strong southerly
OL,10,Fwinds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA mainly cloudy evening and
OL,13,Fnight with further outbreaks of rain
OL,14,Fat times. Fresh to strong southerly
OL,15,Fwinds. A milder night.
OL,16,
OL,17,CFriday:FA mixture of bright or sunny
OL,18,Fintervals and occasional showers.
OL,19,FModerate to fresh southwesterly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
